entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued November 26 at 6:05AM CST by NWS
entry.summary: ...HAZARDOUS TRAVEL POSSIBLE THIS MORNING... Light snow will continue to fall this morning, before diminishing to flurries from west to east in the afternoon. Additional snow accumulations will only be an inch or so in most areas, but it will be enough to produce slippery roads and sidewalks. Take it easy if you are traveling this morning.
